{"tid":956471,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友乜都要AA真係好攰","createTime":"2018-12-26T09:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T22:51:37.000Z","uid":92289,"like":88,"dislike":1564,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"b76edd05cee7cdda0fba46a22fa5b098d46bdd52","tid":956471,"uid":92289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:39:51.000Z","msg":"一開始都覺得佢好好<br />\n因為以前啲ex好似老奉咁要我畀錢<br />\n而佢就食親飯都堅持出一半<br />\n茶記又係同佢鋸扒食貴啲都係<br />\n<br />\n但而家佢好似走火入魔咁<br />\n聖誕節諗住豪啲請佢食餐元氣啦<br />\n佢出咗餐廳門口堅持要畀返我<br />\n仲話帶唔夠現金要payme我<br />\n話請佢食佢又唔肯 係都要我收<br />\n開房買dom都要同我夾錢<br />\n好似我養佢唔起咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我真係寧願佢好似我啲ex咁<br />\n乖乖地等我畀錢<br />\n同我講聲多謝仲開心<br />\n而家大家條數下下都計到咁清<br />\n似朋友多過似拍拖<br />\n<br />\n利申 拍咗半年<br />\n同佢講過呢個問題<br />\n佢話佢老豆由細教佢無功不受祿<br />\n同埋佢唔鍾意爭人錢<br />\n<br />\n點解未來岳父咁識教女<br />\n我想請自己條女食飯啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6daf54090867f7e9e7f64a1b5e14a739e228a05f","tid":956471,"uid":180204,"like":592,"dislike":4,"score":588,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:41:12.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"c8d5bbd485643256d8cf620501345b2e60baf889","tid":956471,"uid":87503,"like":385,"dislike":2,"score":383,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:42:18.000Z","msg":"你女友好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125b53834b25041f4471116b6e42ae99f830cb38","tid":956471,"uid":179292,"like":749,"dislike":2,"score":747,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:42:38.000Z","msg":"唔識珍惜仲要嘈"},{"pid":"51008e54d12b96cdb82a45fd417f3a2338991b05","tid":956471,"uid":77164,"like":1189,"dislike":8,"score":1181,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T09:42:41.000Z","msg":"聖誕節諗住豪啲請佢食餐元氣啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.